o janky that I mostly only invoke it by accident. 1 ( #fn1-12278 ) Part of =
the problem is hardware: there just isn=E2=80=99t that much screen real est=
ate, even on the largest iPad, and the limitation of only using touch contr=
ols means that the operating system has to rely on undiscoverable gestures.

visionOS suffers from a similar combination of shortcomings. First off, the=
