last summer, when I wrote that I suspected the Vision Pro was =E2=80=9Cthe =
future of the Mac=E2=80=9D, and that=E2=80=99s even before getting to the l=
imitations of Apple=E2=80=99s iOS-based operating system in terms of app ca=
pabilities and business models. That latter point, along with the limitatio=
ns of eye-tracking as a default user-interface model, also makes me worry t=
hat new and better hardware won=E2=80=99t change this reality.

