gh unobtrusive glasses to your eyes, with digital information layered over =
the top of what you=E2=80=99re seeing. AR is a technology with the potentia=
l to literally change humanity, and Apple CEO Tim Cook has been talking abo=
ut how isolating VR headsets are and how important he thinks AR will be for=
