=E2=80=9CThis is in many ways better than sitting courtside,=E2=80=9D Silve=
r said Friday. =E2=80=9CIt can take you anywhere on the floor. It can give =
you the perspective of a player =E2=80=A6 This will, to me, be how people o=
ver time experience sports.=E2=80=9D

Actually, no, I do want to sit courtside. It=E2=80=99s one of the most incr=
edible experiences you can have as a fan. Moreover, you don=E2=80=99t even =
need any production: if I want the score, I can look up at the scoreboard; =
the announcer is the in-arena PA system. Don=E2=80=99t overthink this! =E2=
=86=A9=EF=B8=8E ( #rf4-12278 )

